snippet.title: Necromancer Returns Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/632020/

A turn-based strategy game and sequel to the game Beast Battle. The world of a fantasy kingdom has been thrown into disarray by the return of the Necromancer – a creature of darkness that wishes to enslave all living beings.
